window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I was his before he ever caught my scent.</b></p> <p>I used to believe werewolves were no more than scary stories to be told around a campfire. Then, one of them ripped off my clothes, marked me with his teeth, and claimed me like a wild beast.</p> <p>I didn't just come for him. I came until I blacked out, screaming my surrender into the dark Las Vegas night, and when I woke up sore and spent, I knew for certain what I'd only feared before.</p> <p>Kane Lockhart is a monster. And I'm his mate.</p> <p><i>Intended for mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
